**Research findings:**
- Analysis results are ephemeral — `analyze_transcript()` returns `CallAnalysis` to TUI but never persists to disk. Every call re-open re-runs LLM ($$ + latency)
- `Call.tags` always `vec![]` — analysis produces `themes` but never backfills to call
- `build_calls_context()` only sends 200-char transcript preview to agent — persisted analysis summaries/themes would give much higher signal
- CI/CD already exists (`.github/workflows/ci.yml` + `release.yml`) — not the next priority
- Explicitly deferred by call-management and ux-polish specs: "Call tagging UI" + "Cross-call pattern analysis"

